Refunds

General Policy

Customers unsatisfied with StellarLikes’s services may request a refund within the first 30 calendar days from the initial purchase. Refund requests must be initiated through customer support.

Reasons

Our refund policy is applicable under the following circumstances: 1. Non-delivery of the paid service: If you have made a payment for a service and it was not delivered. 2. Multiple charges for a single purchase: In the event that you were erroneously charged multiple times for a single transaction. 3. Incorrect amount charged from the checkout final price: If you were charged an amount that differs from the originally specified checkout final price. 4. The publication date of your post is more than three years ago. Please note that refunds to the original payment method will only be considered for the aforementioned reasons. In all other cases, a refund may be offered as credit to the client’s account balance. It is essential for clients to provide supporting evidence or proofs for refund requests falling within the specified criteria, ensuring a transparent and fair assessment of the situation

Exclusions

Refunds are not eligible for free credits, promotional services, fully delivered and confirmed services, or accounts violating Terms of Service.

Process

To initiate a refund, contact customer support with the order number and a detailed explanation. Approval or denial will be communicated within 3-5 business days. Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method within 7-10 business days.

Right to Deny Refund

StellarLikes reserves the right to deny refunds for abuse, multiple requests, or failure to adhere to terms and conditions.

Service-Specific Guidelines

Once services are fully delivered and confirmed, no refunds are available. Contact customer support for assistance with delivery or quality issues before the 30-day period expires.

Inquiries

Inquiries about this Refund Policy should be directed to customer support via live support By making a purchase on StellarLikes, you agree to this Refund Policy. StellarLikes reserves the right to modify this policy at any time without prior notice.
